In the INTEREST OF J.W., K.W., and G.J., Minor Children, K.W., Mother, Appellant, G.J., Father of G.J., Appellant. No. 19-0372 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Parents separately appeal the termination of their parental rights to their child, and the mother additionally appeals the termination of her parental rights to two of her other children. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
